New chapter for club? 
- Manchester Evening News New chapter for club? 
On January 8, 1887, members of the Heaton Chapel and District Liberal Club walked in procession from their old premises to a brand new purpose-built club. 
Don't miss a thing by getting the latest from the Manchester Evening News sent direct to your inbox Click hereWhen you subscribe we will use the information you provide to send you these newsletters. 
